Written and Directed by Lanlin Wong.

Created for the new 2008 Subaru STi, this video is a rebuttal to the car community's complaints that the new STi had become "domesticated" from its rally/racer background. Our inspiration was that the new model does in fact have the same power, poise, and exclusivity as the outgoing model. It anything, this is one "beast" of a car.
